Use the standard library
This is how to mean_absolute_deviation of numbers:
   Remember that total is 0.000000
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this numbers's length times:
      Remember that total is sum of total and item i in numbers
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that mean is quotient of total and (tofloat of numbers's length)

   Remember that total_deviation is 0.000000
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this numbers's length times:
      Remember that total_deviation is sum of total_deviation and (abs of (diff of item i in numbers and mean))
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is quotient of total_deviation and (tofloat of numbers's length)
Now you know